OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening with some
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells perhaps
OL,9,Fallowing the odd fog patch, somewhat
OL,10,Fcloudier in the southwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,13,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,14,Fsunny spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fagain on Tuesday with variable cloud
OL,18,Fand some warm sunny spells. Variable
OL,19,Fcloud and sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,20,Fand Thursday with the odd light shower
OL,21,Fat times.
